                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/novich/">novich</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-01-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">文字很有节奏和味道，不求大叙事，只有日常点滴里透出的变迁感，多少偏柔弱了些。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1162464249">
        <div class="comment">
